{
  "meta": {
    "format": "vn-package/v1",
    "id": "project.mirror-house",
    "title": "Mirror House",
    "entry": "n000-start",
    "defaultLocale": "en",
    "tags": [],
    "compiler": "thriller/compile-vn-project",
    "sourceLayout": "vn-project/v1"
  },
  "entities": {
    "characters": [
      {
        "id": "char.protagonist",
        "name": "Mara",
        "description": "A skeptical investigative journalist.",
        "defaultExpression": "neutral"
      },
      {
        "id": "char.host",
        "name": "Elias Voss",
        "description": "The owner of the estate, composed and unreadable.",
        "defaultExpression": "calm"
      }
    ],
    "locations": [
      {
        "id": "loc.foyer",
        "name": "Foyer",
        "description": "A cold marble foyer with a locked side door.",
        "background": "bg.foyer"
      },
      {
        "id": "loc.hallway",
        "name": "Hallway",
        "description": "A narrow hall lined with family portraits.",
        "background": "bg.hallway"
      }
    ],
    "variables": [
      {
        "id": "flag.key_found",
        "type": "boolean",
        "default": false
      },
      {
        "id": "trust.host",
        "type": "number",
        "default": 40
      },
      {
        "id": "flag.followed_host",
        "type": "boolean",
        "default": false
      }
    ],
    "assets": [
      {
        "id": "bg.foyer",
        "kind": "background",
        "path": "assets/backgrounds/foyer.png"
      },
      {
        "id": "bg.hallway",
        "kind": "background",
        "path": "assets/backgrounds/hallway.png"
      },
      {
        "id": "bgm.intro",
        "kind": "music",
        "path": "assets/audio/intro.ogg"
      }
    ]
  },
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "e100-locked-out",
      "kind": "ending",
      "title": "Locked Out",
      "location": "loc.foyer",
      "presentation": {
        "background": "bg.foyer"
      },
      "body": [
        {
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "Mara rattles the handle, but the lock refuses to yield."
        }
      ],
      "source": {
        "file": "nodes/e100-locked-out.md",
        "format": "markdown-frontmatter"
      },
      "notes": "# Locked Out"
    },
    {
      "id": "e110-curious-ending",
      "kind": "ending",
      "title": "Curious Ending",
      "location": "loc.hallway",
      "presentation": {
        "background": "bg.hallway"
      },
      "body": [
        {
          "kind": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "char.host",
          "expression": "calm",
          "text": "If you ask the wrong question too early, the house answers instead of me."
        }
      ],
      "source": {
        "file": "nodes/e110-curious-ending.md",
        "format": "markdown-frontmatter"
      },
      "notes": "# Curious Ending"
    },
    {
      "id": "e120-silent-ending",
      "kind": "ending",
      "title": "Silent Ending",
      "location": "loc.hallway",
      "presentation": {
        "background": "bg.hallway"
      },
      "body": [
        {
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "Mara says nothing. The silence becomes its own accusation."
        }
      ],
      "source": {
        "file": "nodes/e120-silent-ending.md",
        "format": "markdown-frontmatter"
      },
      "notes": "# Silent Ending"
    },
    {
      "id": "n000-start",
      "kind": "start",
      "title": "Start",
      "to": "n010-foyer-arrival",
      "source": {
        "file": "nodes/n000-start.md",
        "format": "markdown-frontmatter"
      },
      "notes": "# Start\n\nRuntime entry node. No prose lives here."
    },
    {
      "id": "n010-foyer-arrival",
      "kind": "scene",
      "title": "Foyer Arrival",
      "location": "loc.foyer",
      "presentation": {
        "background": "bg.foyer",
        "music": "bgm.intro"
      },
      "cast": [
        {
          "character": "char.protagonist",
          "expression": "neutral",
          "pose": "standing",
          "position": "left",
          "visible": true
        },
        {
          "character": "char.host",
          "expression": "calm",
          "pose": "standing",
          "position": "right",
          "visible": true
        }
      ],
      "body": [
        {
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "The foyer smells faintly of rain and old varnish."
        },
        {
          "kind": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "char.host",
          "expression": "calm",
          "text": "Welcome. The storm cut the road behind you."
        }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "inspect-door",
          "text": "Inspect the locked side door.",
          "to": "n020-door-check",
          "effects": [
            {
              "op": "set",
              "target": "flag.key_found",
              "value": true
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "follow-host",
          "text": "Follow Elias deeper into the house.",
          "to": "n030-hallway",
          "effects": [
            {
              "op": "set",
              "target": "flag.followed_host",
              "value": true
            },
            {
              "op": "increment",
              "target": "trust.host",
              "value": 10
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "source": {
        "file": "nodes/n010-foyer-arrival.md",
        "format": "markdown-frontmatter"
      },
      "notes": "# Foyer Arrival\n\nUse `scene` for most visual novel moments."
    },
    {
      "id": "n020-door-check",
      "kind": "condition",
      "title": "Door Check",
      "expression": {
        "all": [
          {
            "var": "flag.key_found",
            "op": "eq",
            "value": true
          }
        ]
      },
      "onTrue": "n040-secret-room",
      "onFalse": "e100-locked-out",
      "source": {
        "file": "nodes/n020-door-check.md",
        "format": "markdown-frontmatter"
      },
      "notes": "# Door Check\n\nLogic-only node. No player-facing prose required."
    },
    {
      "id": "n030-hallway",
      "kind": "scene",
      "title": "Hallway",
      "location": "loc.hallway",
      "presentation": {
        "background": "bg.hallway"
      },
      "cast": [
        {
          "character": "char.protagonist",
          "expression": "wary",
          "pose": "walking",
          "position": "center",
          "visible": true
        },
        {
          "character": "char.host",
          "expression": "calm",
          "pose": "walking",
          "position": "right",
          "visible": true
        }
      ],
      "body": [
        {
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "The portraits seem to watch Mara as she walks."
        },
        {
          "kind": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "char.host",
          "expression": "calm",
          "text": "My family had a habit of keeping secrets in plain sight."
        }
      ],
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": "press-host",
          "text": "Ask what he means.",
          "to": "e110-curious-ending"
        },
        {
          "id": "stay-silent",
          "text": "Keep the thought to yourself for now.",
          "to": "e120-silent-ending"
        }
      ],
      "source": {
        "file": "nodes/n030-hallway.md",
        "format": "markdown-frontmatter"
      },
      "notes": "# Hallway\n\nExample of a standard prose node with local choices."
    },
    {
      "id": "n040-secret-room",
      "kind": "ending",
      "title": "Secret Room",
      "location": "loc.foyer",
      "presentation": {
        "background": "bg.foyer"
      },
      "body": [
        {
          "kind": "narration",
          "text": "The door gives way. A hidden room waits behind it, lit by the pulse of an old projector."
        },
        {
          "kind": "dialogue",
          "speaker": "char.host",
          "expression": "calm",
          "text": "You found the version of the story I was trying to bury."
        }
      ],
      "source": {
        "file": "nodes/n040-secret-room.md",
        "format": "markdown-frontmatter"
      },
      "notes": "# Secret Room\n\nTerminal ending node."
    }
  ]
}
